com.github.valid8j.pcond.core.identifieable

Interface Identifiable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExplainablePredicate, Identifiable.Base, InputResolver.Impl, InputResolver.Sequence.Factory.Impl, MultiFunction.Impl, PrintableFunction, PrintablePredicate, PrintablePredicateFactory.Conjunction, PrintablePredicateFactory.Disjunction, PrintablePredicateFactory.StreamPredicate, PrintablePredicateFactory.TransformingPredicate, Proposition.Factory.Impl, PropositionPredicate

    public interface Identifiable

    An interface that represents an object which can be identified based on objects used on instantiation without overriding the Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object). In order to minimize effort to implement this interface, you can extend Identifiable.Base class.
